define.name: E_FMAGGREGATIONERROR
define.abstract: The operation cannot be performed because it will lead to aggregation error.

define.name: E_FMEXCEPTIONRAISED
define.abstract: An unexpected exception has been raised during method call.

define.name: E_FMINVALIDFEATURE
define.abstract: The feature on which method has been called is invalid, NULL or destroyed.

define.name: E_FMKEYNOTFOUND
define.abstract: The attribute is not defined.

define.name: E_FMLOADINGMODE
define.abstract: Access is denied because of a loading mode incompatible with the application.

define.name: E_FMNOLOCALVALUE
define.abstract: There is no local value for a given attribute.

define.name: E_FMNOPLMSESSION
define.abstract: Access is denied because no plm session was found.

define.name: E_FMNOTALIST
define.abstract: Operation cannot be done because attribute is not a list.

define.name: E_FMNOTAPARAMETER
define.abstract: Object does not represent a knowledge parameter.

define.name: E_FMNOTASINGLE
define.abstract: Operation failed because object has a cardinality different from 1.

define.name: E_FMNOTLOADED
define.abstract: The target is not loaded.

define.name: E_FMOPERATIONNOTALLOWED
define.abstract: The operation is not allowed.

define.name: E_FMOPERATIONNOTSUPPORTED
define.abstract: The operation cannot be performed as it is not supported on early features.

define.name: E_FMOUTOFBOUND
define.abstract: Index is outside the bounds of a list.

define.name: E_FMPARAMETER
define.abstract: Access is denied because object represents a knowledge parameter.

define.name: E_FMPRIVATEVALUE
define.abstract: The value is unreachable because private to inherited feature.

define.name: E_FMPROTECTEDRESOURCE
define.abstract: Access is denied because object is runtime resource (for example a Feature Catalog).

define.name: E_FMREADONLY
define.abstract: Access is denied because object is read-only.

define.name: E_FMREDIRECTED
define.abstract: The attribute is redirected to an attribute that cannot be found.

define.name: E_FMTYPEMISMATCH
define.abstract: Operation cannot be done because type does not match.

define.name: E_FMUPDATEERROR
define.abstract: Update has failed.
